# Plan 07-05 fills this directory with:
#   - local-llms.yml  (dashboard provider — declares this dir as a Grafana
#                      dashboard source)
#   - local-llms.json (the actual dashboard with VRAM / TTFT / error-rate /
#                      backend-selection panels per Phase 7 SC4)
#
# Until Plan 07-05 lands, this directory holds only this .gitkeep so:
#   1. git tracks the empty directory;
#   2. the compose.yml bind-mount source path exists at the dir level
#      (the local-llms.json file-bind will create an empty file at
#      `docker compose up` time if Plan 07-05 hasn't landed — Grafana will
#      then fail to parse the empty JSON, but the datasource provisioned in
#      ./datasources/datasource.yml will still be live, which is what
#      Plan 07-02's "datasource alive without dashboard" success criterion
#      asks for).
